</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-03-02-0369-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-03-03-02-0369-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>Congress appointed Stirling a brigadier general on 1 Mar. 1776 (<span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Worthington Chauncey Ford et al., eds. &lt;i&gt;Journals of the Continental Congress, 1774-1789&lt;/i&gt;. 34 vols. Washington, D.C., 190437. ]"><span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">JCC</span></span>, 4:181).</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-03-02-0369-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-03-03-02-0369-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-03-02-0390-0002" class="document">Inventory of British Stores Left in Boston, 20 Mar.</a>,<span class="choice deletion" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover_choice ] header=[]  body=[ Deleted: ' printed below as' &lt;span style='font-size: 90%'&gt;[[2014-12-02]]&lt;/span&gt; ]"><img alt="deletion" src="images/deletion_mark-trans.png" style="border:none;vertical-align: text-bottom; padding-right:2px"/></span> an enclosure to <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-03-02-0390-0001" class="document">GW to Hancock, 24 Mar. 1776</a>, and <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-03-02-0409-0002" class="document">Return of British Ordnance Stores Left in Boston, 22 Mar.</a>, printed as an enclosure to <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-03-02-0409-0001" class="document">GW to Hancock, 27 Mar. 1776</a>.</p>

